{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"handler.has()","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/has","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects\">JavaScript 标准库</a></strong></li><li><strong><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy\"><code>Proxy/handler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></strong></li><li data-default-state=\"open\"><a href=\"#\"><strong>方法</strong></a><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/apply\"><code>handler.apply()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/construct\"><code>handler.construct()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/defineProperty\"><code>handler.defineProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/deleteProperty\"><code>handler.deleteProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/get\"><code>handler.get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/getOwnPropertyDescriptor\"><code>handler.getOwnPropertyDescriptor()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/getPrototypeOf\"><code>handler.getPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><em><code>handler.has()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/isExtensible\"><code>handler.isExtensible()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/ownKeys\"><code>handler.ownKeys()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/preventExtensions\"><code>handler.preventExtensions()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/set\"><code>handler.set()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/setPrototypeOf\"><code>handler.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>&nbsp;<strong><code>handler.has()</code></strong>&nbsp;方法是针对&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/in\"><code>in</code></a> 操作符的代理方法。</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"692\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/proxyhandler-has.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"语法","title":"语法","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">has</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> prop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"参数","title":"参数","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>下面是传递给 has</code>&nbsp;方法的参数。<code>this</code> is bound to the handler.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"target\"><code>target</code></dt>\n <dd>目标对象。</dd>\n <dt id=\"prop\"><code>prop</code></dt>\n <dd>需要检查是否存在的属性。</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"返回值","title":"返回值","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>has</code>&nbsp;方法返回一个 boolean 属性的值。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"描述","title":"描述","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code><strong>handler.has</strong></code> 方法可以看作是针对 <a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/in\"><code>in</code></a> 操作的钩子。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"拦截","title":"拦截","isH3":true,"content":"<p>这个钩子可以拦截下面这些操作：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>属性查询：<code>foo in proxy</code></li>\n <li>继承属性查询：<code>foo in Object.create(proxy)</code></li>\n <li><code>with</code>&nbsp;检查<code>: with(proxy) { (foo); }</code></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Reflect/has\"><code>Reflect.has()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"约束","title":"约束","isH3":true,"content":"<p>如果违反了下面这些规则，proxy 将会抛出&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a>:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>如果目标对象的某一属性本身不可被配置，则该属性不能够被代理隐藏。</li>\n <li>如果目标对象为不可扩展对象，则该对象的属性不能够被代理隐藏</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下面的代码拦截了&nbsp;<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/in\"><code>in</code></a> 操作符。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">has</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> prop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'called: '</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> prop<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'a'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// \"called: a\"</span>\n                       <span class=\"token comment\">// true</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<p>下面的代码违反了约束。</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> obj <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token literal-property property\">a</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nObject<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">preventExtensions</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> p <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Proxy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>obj<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token function-variable function\">has</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">target<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> prop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token string\">'a'</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">in</span> p<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// TypeError is thrown</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"规范","title":"规范","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-proxy-object-internal-methods-and-internal-slots-hasproperty-p\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">[[HasProperty]]</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-proxy-object-internal-methods-and-internal-slots-hasproperty-p\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"zh-CN\">[[HasProperty]]</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.Proxy.handler.has","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/has/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"其他","title":"其他","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy\"><code>Proxy</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy\"><code>handler</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/in\"><code>in</code></a> operator</li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Reflect/has\"><code>Reflect.has()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"语法","id":"语法"},{"text":"描述","id":"描述"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"其他","id":"其他"}],"summary":"handler.has() 方法是针对 in 操作符的代理方法。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"handler.has()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"handler.has()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"handler.has()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/proxy/proxy/has","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/proxy/proxy/has/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"JavaScript 参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"JavaScript 标准内置对象"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy","title":"Proxy"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy","title":"Proxy() 构造器"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Proxy/Proxy/has","title":"handler.has()"}],"pageTitle":"handler.has() - JavaScript | MDN","noIndexing":false}}